    "For each query, the top-1000 candidate passages retrieved by BM25 are reranked.",
    "Latency is measured in seconds per query.enhance retrieval performance, though at the cost of increased latency, suggesting a trade-off between retrieval effectiveness and efficiency.",
    "However, indiscriminately increasing the number of hypothetical documents does not yield significant benefits and substantially raises latency, indicating that using a single hypothetical document is sufficient.",
